  "title" : "Is GSON using a cache mechanism to enhance encoding time for objects",
  "body" : "<p>I'm using GSON Library to encode java objects to JSON Strings and I am interested in how this works. I can suggest that GSON is using a cache mechanism to speedup the encoding, but I can't find a source of knowledge about that topic. In GSON documentation there is no information about it.</p>\n\n<p>Could someone find information about cache behavior of GSON?</p>\n\n<p>Thanks,\nBen</p>\n"
